*Sećam* se svojih prvih dana u školi. (I remember my first days at school.)

Nije mi se *sećala* dobra stara vremena. (She didn't remember the good old days.)

*Sećam* se da sam volio da igram igre. (I remember that I used to love playing games.)

*Sećala* sam se da treba da odem. (I remembered that I had to go.)

Pokušavala je da se *seća* imena. (She was trying to remember the names.)